description: Phoenix comes back for more and is the first to ride the "Fuck-Cycle". The reason there are so few pictures of the action with the Intruder is that the photographer was hanging on to the machine trying to steady it as Phoenix took it full blast. We were amazed at how hard she likes to get fucked, this is just the kind of girl these machines were made for - we feel sorry for the poor bastard that tries to satisfy her.
title: Phoenix
